data.description: Bunker Hill WV!  Close To Travel Route 81, Rt 9, MARK Train, Rt 7, Rt 66!  Colonial All Brick Home Renovated Approximately 2010, And Then Additional Work Completed Within Last 2 Years.  Home Sits On .58 of an Acre And Partially Fenced for Dogs! This Classy Home Boasts The Era Of High Ceilings, Built In Bookcases, Large Open Space Foyer and Traditional Style  Layout With Seperate Living Room, Den, Dining Room, Kitchen. Full Bathroom On The Main Level, Laundry Room Also On Main Level. Upper Level Has 4 Spacious Bedrooms With Closets And Another Full Bath. Both Bathrooms Were Recently Ronovated.  Roof Is A Brand New  50 YearArchitectural Roof As of September 2023.  Whole House Water Treatment System Installed 2022. Leaf Guttering System 2022!  The Home Is Solid and In Very Good Condition. Exterior Cosmetic Masonry Work Completed 2022.. The Exterior Of The Home Has Partial Fencing, Metal Carport And Approximately .58 Acres. Quarterly Pest Contract In Place.
